# Poop Deck :: MQTT ACLs
# Each producer publishes only into its own namespace; the ingest consumer
# reads everything under farm/. Add one stanza per new producer.
#
# Usernames here must match the MQTT_*_USER values in deploy/.env — the
# password file is generated from those at container start.

# The ingest daemon subscribes to every producer's topics.
user ingest
topic read farm/#

# tinkle publishes irrigation run-complete events; nothing else.
user tinkle
topic write farm/irrigation/#
